<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Client Intake — The Holloway Innovation</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@300;400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --black:#0D0D0D;--orange:#E8541A;--o2:#FF7A45;
  --white:#FFFFFF;--gray:#7A8FA6;--dk:#555;
  --mid:#1A1A1A;--border:#2A2A2A;--text:#CCCCCC;
  --green:#27A060;--teal:#3AACB8;
}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--text);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:300;padding-bottom:80px;}
header{background:var(--black);border-bottom:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;align-items:stretch;}
.hbar{width:8px;background:var(--orange);flex-shrink:0;}
.hlogo{padding:10px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.hlogo img{height:80px;width:80px;object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);}
.hdoc{padding:18px 24px;text-align:right;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;border-left:1px solid var(--border);margin-left:auto;}
.hdoc-type{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--white);text-transform:uppercase;}
.hdoc-sub{font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--dk);text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:3px;}
.hdots{display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:8px;}
.hdots span{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;display:block;}
footer{margin-top:60px;border-top:3px solid var(--orange);padding:14px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--mid);}
footer img{height:52px;width:52px;object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);border-radius:4px;}
.ftag{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--dk);text-transform:uppercase;text-align:right;}

.progress-wrap{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:var(--black);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:8px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.p-label{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dk);white-space:nowrap;}
.bar{flex:1;height:3px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;}
.bar-fill{height:100%;background:var(--orange);border-radius:2px;transition:width .3s;width:0%;}
.p-pct{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--orange);min-width:36px;text-align:right;}
.container{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;}
.client-bar{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-top:28px;padding:18px 22px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;}
.field label{display:block;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dk);margin-bottom:5px;}
.field input{background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--white);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;width:100%;padding:3px 0;outline:none;}
.field input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--orange);}
.section{margin-top:32px;}
.section-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.sec-num{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--orange);opacity:.4;line-height:1;min-width:32px;}
.sec-title{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--white);text-transform:uppercase;}
.sec-desc{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--dk);margin-top:1px;}
.divider{flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--border),transparent);}
.checklist{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.item{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:13px 16px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:20px 1fr;gap:13px;align-items:start;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .18s;}
.item:hover{border-color:#3a3a3a;}
.item.checked{border-color:var(--orange);background:#1a0f08;}
.checkbox{width:18px;height:18px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;margin-top:2px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .18s;}
.item.checked .checkbox{background:var(--orange);border-color:var(--orange);}
.item.checked .checkbox::after{content:'✓';color:var(--white);font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;}
.question{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--white);line-height:1.4;}
.why{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--dk);margin-top:3px;font-style:italic;}
.note-input{margin-top:7px;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px dashed var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:.8rem;width:100%;padding:2px 0;outline:none;}
.note-input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--orange);}
.note-input::placeholder{color:#333;}
.tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:7px;}
.tag{font-size:.65rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 9px;color:var(--dk);cursor:pointer;transition:all .14s;user-select:none;}
.tag:hover{border-color:var(--orange);color:var(--o2);}
.tag.on{background:var(--orange);border-color:var(--orange);color:var(--white);font-weight:600;}
.closer{margin-top:36px;background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--orange);border-radius:10px;padding:26px;}
.closer h2{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--orange);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px;}
.pitch-label{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.22em;color:var(--orange);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;margin-top:16px;}
.pitch{font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text);padding:10px 14px;border-left:2px solid var(--orange);background:rgba(232,84,26,.05);border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;}
.summary{margin-top:36px;background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:20px 22px;}
.summary h3{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--dk);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;}
.summary-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
.sum-field label{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dk);display:block;margin-bottom:4px;}
.sum-field input{background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--white);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;width:100%;padding:3px 0;outline:none;}
.sum-field input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--orange);}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="hbar"></div>
  <div class="hlogo">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="The Holloway Innovation">
  </div>
  <div class="hdoc">
    <div class="hdoc-type">Client Intake</div>
    <div class="hdoc-sub">Quote Development Form</div>
    <div class="hdots">
      <span style="background:#E8541A;"></span>
      <span style="background:#fff;"></span>
      <span style="background:#7A8FA6;"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <span class="p-label">Progress</span>
  <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" id="fill"></div></div>
  <span class="p-pct" id="pct">0%</span>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="client-bar">
    <div class="field"><label>Client Name</label><input type="text" placeholder="Full name"></div>
    <div class="field"><label>Phone / Contact</label><input type="text" placeholder="Best number"></div>
    <div class="field"><label>Date</label><input type="text" id="dateField"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header"><div class="sec-num">01</div><div><div class="sec-title">The Space</div><div class="sec-desc">Scope so you can price by area</div></div><div class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What rooms or areas need to be painted?</div><div class="why">💡 Drives labor hours and material estimate</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Living Room</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Bedroom(s)</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Kitchen</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Bathroom(s)</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Hallway</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Basement</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Whole Home</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Other</span></div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="Notes..." onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">How many rooms total, and approximate square footage?</div><div class="why">💡 Determines paint quantity and time on-site</div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="e.g. 3 rooms, ~1,200 sq ft" onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Walls only, or also ceilings and trim?</div><div class="why">💡 Trim and ceilings can double labor time</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Walls only</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Walls + Ceiling</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Walls + Trim</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Everything</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What are the ceiling heights?</div><div class="why">💡 High ceilings require ladders and extra time</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Standard 8ft</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">9–10 ft</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Vaulted / High</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Mixed</span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header"><div class="sec-num">02</div><div><div class="sec-title">Surface Conditions</div><div class="sec-desc">Wall condition affects prep time — biggest pricing variable</div></div><div class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What's the current condition of the walls?</div><div class="why">💡 Holes, cracks, stains require patching/priming — billable prep</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Good / Clean</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Minor scuffs</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Multiple repairs</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Heavy damage</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Has it been painted before, and what color is it now?</div><div class="why">💡 Dark-to-light transitions need extra coats</div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="Current color / finish..." onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Any water damage, mold, or smoke stains?</div><div class="why">💡 Requires specialty primer — note liability</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">None</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Water stains</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Smoke / nicotine</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Mold (refer out)</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Any wallpaper that needs to be removed?</div><div class="why">💡 Wallpaper removal is a separate billable service</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">No wallpaper</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Yes — needs removal</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Painting over it</span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header"><div class="sec-num">03</div><div><div class="sec-title">Paint Preferences</div><div class="sec-desc">Material cost and finish requirements</div></div><div class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Do you have paint picked out, or need recommendations?</div><div class="why">💡 If you're supplying paint, factor into price</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">I'll supply it</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Need recommendations</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Have color, you buy</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What finish are you looking for?</div><div class="why">💡 Sheen affects coverage and coats needed</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Flat / Matte</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Eggshell</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Satin</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Semi-gloss</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Not sure</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">How many colors are you going for?</div><div class="why">💡 Multiple colors = more masking and cleanup</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">One throughout</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Different per room</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Accent wall(s)</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Still deciding</span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header"><div class="sec-num">04</div><div><div class="sec-title">Logistics & Timeline</div><div class="sec-desc">Access and scheduling details</div></div><div class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Is anyone living in the space during work?</div><div class="why">💡 Occupied homes require more protection</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Occupied</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Vacant</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Partially occupied</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Are rooms empty or will furniture need to be moved?</div><div class="why">💡 Moving/covering furniture adds labor — charge for it</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Empty rooms</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Some furniture</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Fully furnished</span></div></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What's your ideal start date or timeframe?</div><div class="why">💡 Rush jobs may carry a premium</div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="e.g. ASAP, end of month, flexible..." onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Easy parking / access to the property?</div><div class="why">💡 Difficult access adds setup time</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Easy access</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Some restrictions</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">High-rise / stairs</span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header"><div class="sec-num">05</div><div><div class="sec-title">Budget & Expectations</div><div class="sec-desc">Qualify the lead before quoting</div></div><div class="divider"></div></div>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Do you have a budget range in mind?</div><div class="why">💡 Helps you pitch the right package</div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="Budget range or 'flexible'..." onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">Have you gotten other quotes?</div><div class="why">💡 Tells you who you're competing with</div><input class="note-input" type="text" placeholder="Notes on competition..." onclick="stop(event)"></div></div>
      <div class="item" onclick="toggle(this)"><div class="checkbox"></div><div><div class="question">What matters most — price, speed, or quality?</div><div class="why">💡 Reveals how to position your value in the close</div><div class="tags"><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Best price</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">Done fast</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">High quality finish</span><span class="tag" onclick="tag(event,this)">All three</span></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="closer">
    <h2>The Close — Script Phrases</h2>
    <div class="pitch-label">After collecting info — transition to value</div>
    <div class="pitch">"Based on everything you've shared, I have a clear picture of what this project needs. At Holloway Innovation, we don't just paint — we prep right, protect your space, and make sure the finish lasts. Let me put together a quote that reflects exactly what you described."</div>
    <div class="pitch-label">Set the next step</div>
    <div class="pitch">"I'd love to do a quick walkthrough so I can give you an accurate number — no surprises. Can we set something up this week? I have [day] or [day] available."</div>
    <div class="pitch-label">If they're price-shopping</div>
    <div class="pitch">"I get it — you want a fair deal. What I can promise is transparency: I'll show you exactly what you're paying for, and I stand behind the work. A lot of people call me back after going with the cheapest option. I'd rather earn your trust upfront."</div>
    <div class="pitch-label">Soft close</div>
    <div class="pitch">"I'll get your quote over within 24–48 hours. Once you review it, I just need a deposit to lock in your dates — spots fill up quick. Sound good?"</div>
  </div>
  <div class="summary">
    <h3>Quote Summary Notes</h3>
    <div class="summary-grid">
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Rooms / Sq Ft</label><input type="text"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Prep Level</label><input type="text" placeholder="Low / Med / High"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Coats Needed</label><input type="text"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Est. Hours</label><input type="text"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Materials Cost</label><input type="text" placeholder="$"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Labor Cost</label><input type="text" placeholder="$"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Quote Total</label><input type="text" placeholder="$"></div>
      <div class="sum-field"><label>Follow-Up Date</label><input type="text"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<footer>
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="The Holloway Innovation">
  <div>
    <div class="ftag">Interior Painting · Cleveland, OH · Licensed &amp; Insured</div>
  </div>
</footer>
<script>
document.getElementById('dateField').value=new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US',{month:'short',day:'numeric',year:'numeric'});
const all=document.querySelectorAll('.item');
function upd(){const n=document.querySelectorAll('.item.checked').length;const p=Math.round(n/all.length*100);document.getElementById('fill').style.width=p+'%';document.getElementById('pct').textContent=p+'%';}
function toggle(el){el.classList.toggle('checked');upd();}
function stop(e){e.stopPropagation();}
function tag(e,el){e.stopPropagation();el.classList.toggle('on');}
</script>
</body>
</html>
